### Problem Description

While we can index and search via knn with a hexadecimal string when vectors are indexed via bytes, we cannot use script score. 

### Steps to Reproduce

```
DELETE byte_vectors

PUT byte_vectors
{
  "mappings": {
    "properties": {
      "vector": {
        "type": "dense_vector",
        "index": false,
        "element_type": "byte",
        "dims": 128
      }
    }
  }
}


