https://gradle-enterprise.elastic.co/s/zpuwiiomt72u4/tests/:qa:mixed-cluster:v7.17.22%23mixedClusterTest/org.elasticsearch.backwards.SearchWithMinCompatibleSearchNodeIT/testMinVersionAsOldVersion


